# Responsible Social Media Use Checklist for College Students

## Do's
- Think before you post
- Use strong passwords and enable privacy settings
- Share accurate and verified information
- Be respectful and polite in online interactions
- Use social media for learning and networking

## Don'ts
- Do not share personal or sensitive information publicly
- Avoid posting offensive or harmful content
- Do not spread fake news or rumors
- Avoid cyberbullying or negative comments
- Do not spend excessive time on social media
